{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>M.E.M.O demo (\u03b1)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to <strong>M.E.M.O demo (\u03b1)</strong> where you can get a sneak peek into the world of &quot;M.E.M.O&quot;!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While some features are yet to be implemented in this version, you can already experience the captivating world setting and core cryptography gameplay that makes &quot;M.E.M.O&quot; special.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u203bPlease have paper and pen ready when playing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u203bThe demo(\u03b2) is scheduled for release in July 2025.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u203bThis demo may differ from the final product.<br><br>\u203bThe screenshots shown are all from the development stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972940/extras/Steam_bar.png?t=1736865988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;In the dark, swaying train, you awaken to the sound of a red telephone, having lost your memory...&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972940/extras/Steam_bar.png?t=1736865988\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972940/extras/Story.png?t=1736865988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In 2176, Shin Japan is plagued by various social issues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Amidst this, a terrorist organization called &quot;OUKAMI&quot; threatens the government with the release of a deadly virus nationwide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a chosen agent, you must dive into the memories of the deceased to prevent this terror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Retro landscapes of the mind, cryptic codes guarding old secrets, the truth of a world collapse 100 years ago...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wandering through the maze of memories, can you find the key to save the future?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972940/extras/Steam_bar.png?t=1736865988\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972940/extras/Features.png?t=1736865988\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Graphics depicting retro Japanese landscapes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A game experience that allows for genuine code-breaking using <strong>pen and paper</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A suspense story blending historical events with science fiction</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972940/extras/Steam_bar.png?t=1736865988\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2972940?t=1736865988","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972940/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1736865988","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972940/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736865988","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972940/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736865988","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3102200,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>M.E.M.O demo (\u03b1)</